ities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a freak\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"a-lifetime\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Earth's climate warms and becomes more extreme, news of wildfires devouring the Mediterranean is becoming as predictable as mud atGlastonbury.\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Earth's climate warms\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"wildfires\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"the Mediterranean\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"mud atGlastonbury\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This poses a problem for the modern summer Olympics, because many cities in the world willsoon simply be too hotfor athletes to safely compete, and for spectators to watch them.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern summer Olympics\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"many cities\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"the world willsoon\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"hotfor athletes\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It means either the pool of potential hosts will shrink to only those in most temperate areas, or there will need to be big changes like events being mainly held indoors, or no longer taking place in August.\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"potential hosts\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"most temperate areas\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"big changes\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"indoors\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Love fromShade the UK, a London-based campaign group and community interest company, told Metro.co.uk that it's 'not a case of just saying cities hotter than us will not be able to have the Olympics, but it's more that there are cities that are not ready for warmer temperatures and might not be able to handle it'.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 990, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Love\", \"score\": 0.9999999942720024, \"rank\": 5.726773800161342e-09, \"text\": \"Andy Love\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Love\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Love\"}, {\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999758041152333, \"rank\": 2.4187821595080622e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"score\": 0.9993608704168107, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Metro.co.uk\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_(British_newspaper)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a London-based campaign group\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"community interest company\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"a case\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"warmer temperatures\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some cities, such as Qatar for the last World Cup, have searing temperatures but the money to install industrial-strength air conditioning, making it just about possible host major sporting events.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\", \"score\": 0.9990991190779908, \"rank\": 0.0009016932403481344, \"text\": \"Qatar\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some cities\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"the last World Cup\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"searing temperatures\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"industrial-strength air conditioning\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"possible host major sporting events\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If energy-intensive cooling systems become required to make the Games tolerable, however, this would rule out many poorer countries and cause a damaging impact in terms of sustainability.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"energy-intensive cooling systems\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"many poorer countries\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"a damaging impact\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The red areas on the map below show areas projected to see significant changes in climate between 2041 and 2070.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The red areas\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"the map\", \"from\": 171