a.\", \"from\": 5109, \"to\": 5214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5169, \"end\": 5174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.995125218666793, \"rank\": 0.004821586338093347, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Projected temperatures\", \"from\": 5109, \"to\": 5131}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 5176, \"to\": 5182}, {\"ngram\": \"southern Europe\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5199}, {\"ngram\": \"East Asia\", \"from\": 5204, \"to\": 5213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The simplest solution, and one which has already been done, is to change the date.\", \"from\": 5216, \"to\": 5298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The simplest solution\", \"from\": 5216, \"to\": 5237}, {\"ngram\": \"the date\", \"from\": 5289, \"to\": 5297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the summer events have almost always been held in July and August for over 50 years, this is peak summer for many of the potential host cities.\", \"from\": 5300, \"to\": 5449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the summer events\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5323}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 5356, \"to\": 5360}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 5365, \"to\": 5371}, {\"ngram\": \"over 50 years\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5389}, {\"ngram\": \"peak summer\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5410}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential host cities\", \"from\": 5423, \"to\": 5448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser thatsupports HTML5 video Up Next The summer Olympics may become more of an autumn Olympics, pushed forward to late September, like when it was hosted bySeoulin 1988 andSydneyin 2000.\", \"from\": 5451, \"to\": 5735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5484, \"end\": 5494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8488096058593675e-20, \"text\